# Security Policy

Vision takes security seriously.

---

## Reporting Vulnerabilities

If you discover a security issue:

- Do NOT open a public issue
- Do NOT disclose details publicly
- Contact the maintainers privately

(https://discord.gg/P7pSSHuBjD)

---

## Scope

In scope:
- Consensus flaws
- P2P attacks
- Remote crashes
- Chain safety violations

Out of scope:
- DoS from malformed configs
- Local machine issues
- Experimental or disabled features

---

## Response Timeline

- Acknowledgement within 72 hours
- Fix timeline depends on severity
- Credit given where appropriate

Thank you for helping keep Vision safe.
